Class MatchEntity.ParticipantEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mingweisamuel.zyra.entity.Entity

    MatchEntity

    public class MatchEntity.ParticipantEntity
extends Entity
    A entity representation of a participantInfo in a single match. May or may not be associated with a SummonerEntity.

        public SummonerEntity getSummonerEntity()
        Gets the summoner entity who played as this participantInfo.

        May return cached SummonerEntity instance as described in EntityApi.getSummonerFromPlayer(Player).
        Returns:
        The summoner entity. May be null if summoner entity doesn't exist. This occurs when matches do not include identity information which usually means the match was unranked.

        public CompletableFuture<SortedMap<Long,MatchParticipantFrame>> getTimelineAsync()
        Returns:
        A CompletableFuture for this participant's timeline, which is a map from timestamps (long) to MatchParticipantFrames. The map is sorted in chronological order (ascending timestamps).

      • getTimeline

        public SortedMap<Long,MatchParticipantFrame> getTimeline()
        Returns:
        This participant's timeline, which is a map from timestamps (long) to MatchParticipantFrames. The map is sorted in chronological order (ascending timestamps).
